0c3e2c2d571cd9af9748f79","date":"2026-02-26 05:48:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深入探讨了端侧大模型如何重塑移动操作系统，涵盖了从 GUI 智能体训练、系统级服务调度到面向 NPU 的全栈推理优化及软硬垂直协同的未来愿景。","summary":"文章整理自北京邮电大学徐梦炜博士在 QCon 的演讲实录，系统性地阐述了端侧大模型带来的技术范式转移。作者指出，端侧 AI 已从传统的独立任务优化演进为以智能助手为核心的系统级工程。在应用层，提出了利用无标注 GUI 轨迹进行逆动力学训练的方法，以解决智能体标注成本高和长程操作成功率低的问题；在系统层，分析了大模型作为系统服务“下沉”后的 LoRA 兼容性与多任务调度挑战；在硬件层，分享了自研推理引擎 mllm 在非 CUDA NPU 上的优化实践，包括解决动态 shape 和量化离群值等痛点。最后，作者展望了软硬一体化、牺牲通用性以换取极致能效的垂直协同设计方向。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_a9e947c8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_c16f8d46","title":"容器运行时迁移有大坑！Netflix 的 CPU 架构瓶颈排查与修复实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMjYzNjkzNw==&mid=2247634629&idx=1&sn=cca8c23b8cb9ef41ee85d53e4ca8bf66","date":"2026-02-24 23:16:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c16f8d46.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"dbaplus社群","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":20,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_97909516","title":"知识引导","link":"https://martinfowler.com/articles/reduce-friction-ai/knowledge-priming.html","date":"2026-02-24 14:40:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_97909516.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Martin Fowler","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":10,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_08470002","title":"达利欧最新长文：2026，像极了 1936","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIxNTAzNzU0Ng==&mid=2654903821&idx=1&sn=40f0a870f61197d0a83c71ea9add1fb2","date":"2026-02-25 13:31:00","oneSentenceSummary":"瑞·达利欧通过“大周期”框架分析指出，当前世界秩序正处于从有序向严重失序转弯的临界点，2026 年的地缘政治与经济态势与 1936 年高度相似。","summary":"本文基于瑞·达利欧的最新长文，系统阐述了全球秩序正进入“大周期”中的第六阶段——大失序时期。达利欧认为，1945 年后的世界秩序已瓦解，国际关系回归“强权即公理”的丛林法则。文章通过回顾 1930 年代的经济大萧条、民粹主义兴起及二战爆发的历程，揭示了债务周期、内部秩序和外部秩序三大力量如何交织并导致冲突。他详细拆解了贸易、科技、资本、地缘政治和军事五种战争形式，并警示当前全球正处于从前四种“冷”战争向热战滑落的边缘。最后，他提出了在动荡周期中保护财富的逻辑，即看好黄金、警惕债务，并呼吁通过双赢谈判避免“愚蠢的战争”。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_08470002.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"笔记侠","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":48,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_b44c49bb","title":"深度｜OpenAI API 华人工程负责人：模型会把你的脚手架当早餐吃掉，为模型的未来而构建，而非为模型的当下而构建","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&mid=2247514229&idx=1&sn=9151883fbb173dc18061de3d56e9be20","date":"2026-02-24 03:19:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_b44c49bb.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Z Potentials","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":97,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_4a540ab","title":"在 AI 时代打造世界级工程团队 - The Pragmatic Summit","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fYh1CWadxDM","date":"2026-02-24 16:15:09","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_4a540ab.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The Pragmatic Engineer","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":22,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_ab2f755","title":"AI 如何重塑软件构建工艺 - The Pragmatic Summit","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bo6Gtq3nMXc","date":"2026-02-23 20:43:53","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ab2f755.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The Pragmatic Engineer","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":32,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_64fc2a7","title":"Builders Unscripted：第 1 集 - OpenClaw 创始人 Peter Steinberger","link":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9jgcT0Fqt7U","date":"2026-02-24 17:03:32","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_64fc2a7.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"OpenAI","resourceType":"VIDEO","readTime":37,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_8d728e4","title":"#434.AI 时代的生存法则：纳瓦尔谈氛围编程、个人杠杆与创造力的未来","link":"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/699dec62de29766da968a099","date":"2026-02-24 23:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8d728e4.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"跨国串门儿计划","resourceType":"PODCAST","readTime":7,"score":93}]
